{"tid":1592051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【製造話題】【有圖】如果送花比記者會點？","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:50:51.000Z","uid":184099,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20910f5d4a211871be713b05a2b79aab96184ae4","tid":1592051,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最近多左post話外國人對香港既示威已經開始乏味。<br />\n但又無提出解決辦法。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家小弟有少少立idea，唔知大家覺得點。<br />\n<br />\n首先，我讚成示威不是嘉年華，<br />\n但無可否認既係，某些舉動起外國都有迴響。<br />\n有時候一個舉動比外國報道，<br />\n勝過千言萬語既文宣。<br />\n<br />\n例如：【睇圖】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59is7Dx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59is7Dx.jpg&h=5ef85ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBNxziy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBNxziy.jpg&h=d9a4325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdUoFYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdUoFYy.jpg&h=6906275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEhQ5qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEhQ5qe.jpg&h=a85c4135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irEcziz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirEcziz.jpg&h=e0509251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖所見，<br />\n【靚女護士pepe，樓梯pepe人鏈，美國隊長，蜘蛛俠，同埋幫記者帶頭盔】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢d起外國都好大迴響，勝過千言萬語之文宣。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁不如，929個日，<br />\n我地齊齊折朵玫瑰送比記者？</span></span></strong><br />\n起玫瑰條枝度附上紙條，<br />\n中英寫d辛苦了，然後寫d文宣。<br />\n<br />\n聽落可能好膠，但我覺得係ok既。<br />\n大家覺得點？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zgnd3dR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZgnd3dR.jpg&h=67243e5c&